    "基本TTS: デバイスの標準音声で即座に再生できます。保存は不要です。": {
      "comment": "A description of the basic TTS option, explaining that it uses the device's built-in audio for immediate playback and does not require saving.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Basic TTS: Plays instantly with the device's standard voice. No saving required."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TTS básico: reproduce al instante con la voz estándar del dispositivo. No se requiere guardado."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Basis-TTS: Sofortige Wiedergabe mit der Standardstimme des Geräts. Kein Speichern erforderlich."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TTS de base : Lecture instantanée avec la voix standard de l'appareil. Aucune sauvegarde requise."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TTS base: Riproduzione istantanea con la voce standard del dispositivo. Non è necessario salvare."
